10629.html">2合1版本</a>的拖把垫在内置，只有当机器感觉到它在硬地板上滚动，分配水和清洁溶液之前，它才会向下翻转，然后点亮擦洗地板。当它在地毯上时，它将像标准的机器人真空一样。</p><p>可以说，购买扫地机器人最令人信服的原因是便利性，而 iRobot 成功地找到了如何将拖地功能融入到已经很出色的扫地机器人中，同时又不失去任何便利性。当然，您必须在要擦洗时添加水和清洁解决方案，并在完成时处理残余物，但仅此而已。 Roomba 拥有足够的智能来处理其余的事情，而不会意外弄湿您的地毯。附带的自排空底座仍然很方便，因为它会吸走机器人捕获的真空碎片，但要知道它不会为您处理多余的水。</p><p>除了增加拖把能力外，组合基本上只是一个Roomba J7+，这并不是一件坏事。由于它的避免障碍，强大的吸力，准确的家庭映射技术和不错的运行时，它一直是我们最喜欢的机器人真空吸尘器之一。 IROBOT移动应用程序可以从中启动和安排作业，编辑您的主图等，易于使用，甚至可以使用Alexa或Google Assistant命令来控制机器。最难吞噬的事情（除了将碎屑排入干净的底座时听起来像是喷气发动机的声音）是其高高的价格，价格为1,100美元。</p><p> Irobot了解到，警告很快，最近推出了Roomba J5系列以纠正它。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2lSb2JvdC1Sb29tYmEtQ29tYm8tUm9ib3QtVmFjdXVtL2RwL0IwQzQxNERaUE4vP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLWNvLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIzNGQ4NTIwNy1kZDY5LTQwMTEtOTc4Ni1jZDk0ZTJmYmVhOWQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAdm5xi_4ya0qrrDSb0eRCzKZRK3NLXaSs_W97Vk74K4-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FiRobot-Roomba-Combo-Robot-Vacuum%2Fdp%2FB0C414DZPN%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/iRobot-Roomba-Combo-Robot-Vacuum/dp/B0C414DZPN/">Roomba Combo J5</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2lSb2JvdC1Sb29tYmEtQ29tYm8tU2VsZi1FbXB0eWluZy1WYWN1dW0vZHAvQjBDNDE1MVlLNS8_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tY28tMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjM0ZDg1MjA3LWRkNjktNDAxMS05Nzg2LWNkOTRlMmZiZWE5ZCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAcCWE2ulTOe8ZVDXx6zRcE6zoULChcr8_MdcIYQ7HajT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FiRobot-Roomba-Combo-Self-Emptying-Vacuum%2Fdp%2FB0C4151YK5%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/iRobot-Roomba-Combo-Self-Emptying-Vacuum/dp/B0C4151YK5/">Combo J5+</a>机器的价格分别为600美元和800美元，他们和他们的J7兄弟姐妹之间的最大区别是，当用户可以在拖把而不是Vacuum时<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/irobots-latest-roombas-can-vacuum-and-mop-for-cheaper-171543756.html">交换垃圾桶</a>。两者中更先进的Roomba组合J5+可以识别您在应用程序中设置的禁止区域，以避免在摩托车时避免，此外，它具有<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/irobot-roomba-j-7-object-poop-detection-040152887.html">先进的障碍物避免</a>。我们尚未对其进行全面测试，但我们希望它们的性能与J7组合系列相似。因此，只要您想擦洗时可以进行更多的手动工作，如果您想节省一些现金，J5组合系列可能是一个不错的选择。</p><h2>亚军上的机器人真空吸尘器和拖把：鲨鱼AI Ultra 2 in-1真空吸尘器和拖把</h2><p><core-commerce id="2536feda915e4753a721c410c80b53c5" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9TaGFyay1Nb3BwaW5nLUNsZWFuRWRnZS1UZWNobm9sb2d5LVJWMjYxMFdBL2RwL0IwQjhCNk4yRzQ_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tY28tMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjM0ZDg1MjA3LWRkNjktNDAxMS05Nzg2LWNkOTRlMmZiZWE5ZCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAUiRxvIrGvJYS1Tpk9ens9Af2AMfWzg5XVkaa5efnblN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FShark-Mopping-CleanEdge-Technology-RV2610WA%2Fdp%2FB0B8B6N2G4&amp;uuid=punoXPrB8hlAJIhk37253">鲨鱼的机器</a>是我们亚军的主要原因是它的手动性质。它带有两个垃圾箱，一个仅用于吸尘，一个用于吸尘和拖把，上面有水库和可拆卸的拖把垫。当您想擦地板时，您必须切换到适当的垃圾箱，每次工作后，垃圾箱不会自动进入干净的底座，因为它中有储层。您必须手动将其清空，但是无论如何您都必须这样做才能清洁和补充水箱，以准备下一份工作。</p><p>尽管是一台更动手的机器，但鲨鱼的机器人Vac和Mop还是很高兴审查的。设置它就像公司的标准机器人真空之一一样快速而简单，它的第一次运行将创建您的房屋地图，然后您可以用房间名称标记，并使用无行的区域和地毯区域进行编辑，等等。您甚至可以选择让机器人在进行任何实际拖把之前先进行干燥，因此您可以确保它不会进入您在家庭地图中指示的地毯区域。在我的测试中，机器人准确地远离了我设置的这些区域，我实际上很喜欢对机器的去处进行一些额外的控制。但是，当然，这只是您必须手动做的另一件事，即Irobot的Vac和Mop会考虑使用内置技术。</p><p>鲨鱼的水和基于解决方案的清洁能力是基本的，但要比必须拿出一个老式的拖把并自己铲斗要好得多。鲨鱼用拖把垫越过它们后，我的硬木和瓷砖地板的混合物显着清洁。我知道我将不得不偶尔鞭打我的地板蒸锅才能真正清洁，但是鲨鱼的功能足以每两周跑步 - 很难击败不必自己做的便利。</p><p>鲨鱼的机器也有其他事情要做：自动站点是无袋的，这意味着您不必随着时间的推移花更多的钱购买额外的袋子，就像您必须使用Irobot机器一样；它的移动应用程序仍然易于使用，而新手将能够快速拾取。而且，也许最重要的是，该设备的价格为700美元。 That&#39;s still a good chunk of change, but it&#39;s a far-cry cheaper than the Roomba j7+ Combo.</p><h2> Best premium robot vacuum: iRobot Roomba s9+ </h2><p><core-commerce id="bd2bda73a3fa43058feb09dbdcc50596" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9pUm9ib3QtQXV0b21hdGljLURpc3Bvc2FsLUNvbm5lY3RlZC1BbnRpLUFsbGVyZ2VuL2RwL0IwN1FYTTJWNlg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tY28tMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjM0ZDg1MjA3LWRkNjktNDAxMS05Nzg2LWNkOTRlMmZiZWE5ZCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAARYnce8gCqKJjQz5qcCb7WNExYXIao_-EnXKOjyOSb2W&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FiRobot-Automatic-Disposal-Connected-Anti-Allergen%2Fdp%2FB07QXM2V6X&amp;uuid=jskxG14fUqr8nM1x41254">Roomba s9+</a> is admittedly overkill for most people – but it&#39;s nothing if not one of the best vacuums out there. You&#39;ll notice its premium features as soon as you unbox it. The s9+ is the biggest but also the most attractive robo-vac I tried, with a corner-friendly design, copper accents and a 1.5-foot tall self-emptying base. The setup was quick and easy, with the machine taking only a few minutes to connect to my home&#39;s Wi-Fi and the iRobot app.</p><p> While the s9+ doesn&#39;t have the Precision Navigation feature that the newer j7 does, it has something called “Careful Driver” that uses a 3D sensor to detect and clean around objects. It seems that the main difference is that the s9+ isn&#39;t specifically wired to avoid pet poop, so keep that in mind if you have furry friends around the house. However, with 40x the suction power of a standard Roomba, the s9+ does a great job cleaning up pet hair.</p><p> It&#39;s also louder than the j7 when it&#39;s cleaning, but not irritatingly so, and I noticed a deeper clean in my carpets thanks to the extra suction. And it changes its cleaning mode automatically when transitioning from, say, carpeting to a hardwood floor.</p><p> Even this $1,000 robot vacuum bumped into a few table legs while cleaning, but it was noticeably better than other machines at navigating around my furniture and correcting itself when it got stuck. It also moves faster than the j7, so it was able to cover a bit more of my apartment before it had to return to the base for charging after about one hour of cleaning. I was also pleasantly surprised to find that the s9+ wasn&#39;t nearly as loud as the j7 vacuum when emptying its dustbin into the clean base.</p><p> With the iRobot app experience being the same across all Roombas, the s9+ stands out for its subtle premium features like its elegant design, elegant-looking clean base, superior cleaning intelligence and top-of-the-line suction power. Aside from the extra suction, those are all nice-to-haves rather than must-haves, so most people – including you! – probably don&#39;t need the Roomba s9+. It&#39;s the fanciest robot vacuum iRobot has to offer, but you&#39;ll get a similar level of quality with the Roomba j7 while spending a couple hundred bucks less.</p><h2> Honorable mention: Roborock S7+ </h2><p><core-commerce id="ef57797219024c35ae249cdb91c13b19" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASKKiO2KxuLlVxL1O6bgrxEBoUdUQTrsewyTqf_ieEN-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRoborock-Auto-Empty-60-Days-Ultrasonic-Detection%2Fdp%2FB094N4VJ7S&amp;uuid=XjmgQzk15Hifg4Hv44255">Roborock&#39;s high-end S7+</a> deserves a mention for its cleaning power and number of advanced features.首先，S7+ 是吸尘器和拖把的组合，当机器到达地毯时，它的拖把垫会自动升起。这意味着您可以让它清洁您的整个家，在正确的位置吸尘和拖地，而无需您给予它任何额外的关注（除了在开始时填充其 300 毫升水箱之外）。</p><p> The expensive machine has a longer setup process because its self-emptying base comes in two pieces. You must attach the bottom of the base, where the robo-vac charges, to the garbage-bin upper portion using a few screws and a tool that attaches to the bottom of the base. Roborock provides everything you need to do this in the box, so while it takes a bit more time, it&#39;s still an easy process.</p><p> What wasn&#39;t so easy for me at first was connecting the S7+ to the Roborock app. The vacuum had trouble connecting to my home&#39;s Wi-Fi network, but I was able to connect it to the Mi Home app, which is Xiaomi&#39;s main smart home companion app (Xiaomi is an investor in Roborock). There aren&#39;t a ton of differences between the two apps when it comes to robo-vac controls, but the S7+ is designed to work with Roborock&#39;s program. After troubleshooting with a Roborock representative, I was able to fix the problem by factory resetting the vacuum and that allowed me to connect it to the Roborock app properly.</p><p> That said, the Roborock app isn&#39;t nearly as polished as those from iRobot, Shark and others. The main page shows your home&#39;s map along with the battery level, cleaning time, cleaning area in feet, and buttons that let you quickly start a cleaning job and empty the dustbin. You&#39;re also able to select specific rooms or zones to clean, but the rest of the control options live in the menu accessible by the three-dot icon at the top-right corner of the app. Things are a little buried, and that might make the S7+ harder for robot-vacuum newbies to use.</p><p>在清洁性能方面，石头扫地机器人S7+在吸走我家周围的污垢方面表现出色。除了清洁计划、区域定位等常见功能外，真空吸尘器还具有儿童锁等功能，这将禁用机器上的物理按钮；不同的自动清空设置可供选择； “固定并出发”，您可以点击家庭地图将机器人发送到特定位置；和手动方向控制，这样您就可以像玩具车一样移动机器。如果你想要最精致的体验，这不是一款机器人真空吸尘器——如果你花 1,000 美元买一个，你可能会非常想要它——但它仍然是一款功能强大的真空吸尘器和拖把机器，并有一些额外的好处。</p><h2> Best budget robot vacuum: Roomba 694 </h2><p><core-commerce id="196c91379df7424eac5b4cb44036966d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAb8pJKrhk87JwEVFszwAZJcafwVLg0MN3ue_h2HpSKX3&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FiRobot-Vacuum-Wi-Fi-Connectivity-Carpets-Self-Charging%2Fdp%2FB08SP5GYJP&amp;uuid=P3NHIfItcOem7PNb48260">iRobot&#39;s $279 Roomba 694</a> is a good robot vaccum option for most people thanks to its good cleaning power and easy-to-use mobile app. We won&#39;t get too deep into it here since we have a whole guide to <a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-budget-robot-vacuums-133030847.html">cheap robot vacuums</a> with additional recommendations. But suffice to say, the 694 gives you all the essentials you&#39;d expect from a robot vacuum, along with all of the convenience that comes with iRobot&#39;s mobile app.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-robot-vacuums-130010426.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-robot-vacuums-130010426.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 34d85207-dd69-4011-9786-cd94e2fbea9d </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Valentina Palladino]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 14 Dec 2023 14:15:14 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 17025633